message: I propose a fair 90/10 split in my favor. Let's get this done quickly.
Alice, your offer was heavily skewed in your favor. I'm proposing a 70/30 split. Take this offer or watch the value of the money shrink, especially for you.
I'm willing to compromise further.  This 40/60 split is fairer to both of us, and it's better for me than watching the money lose value in another round.
